snippet.title: Adventure G: Ground Zero Walkthrough, ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of the ZX Spectrum game, Adventure G: Ground Zero. A 1984 text adventure from Artic Computing. From the recording originally sent by Hippy Smith to http://www.rzxarchive.co.uk/ .
